{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781966772066,"sessionID":"ses_11a818b5dffer2YDz4na8QwbBS","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"336078005","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Cache API\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance with an internal `Map` for storing key-value pairs.\n\n```js\nimport { createCache } from 'path/to/cache'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n// cache is now an object with get, set, delete, and clear methods\n```\n\n### Methods\n\nThe `createCache()` function returns an object with the following methods:\n\n#### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by its key. Returns the cached value if found, otherwise `undefined`.\n\n```js\ncache.get('my-key')\n```\n\n#### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache under the specified key. Returns the provided value.\n\n```js\ncache.set('my-key', 'my-value')\n```\n\n#### delete(key)\n\nRemoves an entry from the cache by its key. Returns `true` if the key existed, `false` otherwise.\n\n```js\ncache.delete('my-key')\n```\n\n#### clear()\n\nEmpties the entire cache, removing all key-value pairs.\n\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```js\nimport { createCache } from 'cache.mjs'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n\ncache.set('user:1', { id: 1, name: 'Alice' })\nconst user = cache.get('user:1')\ncache.delete('user:1')\ncache.clear()\n```\n","filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-20T06-38-17-288Z/dcp-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-20T06-38-17-288Z/dcp-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","time":{"start":1781966772046,"end":1781966772058}},"id":"prt_ee57ef6b4001RkljWRpIlN0Mwy","sessionID":"ses_11a818b5dffer2YDz4na8QwbBS","messageID":"msg_ee57ef2d2001EjeEohLE0d4sK6"}}
